{
  "id": "terra",
  "name": "Terra",
  "tagline": "Warm organic earthen light",
  "description": "Aesop-counter calm for business dashboards: sand and linen surfaces, deep soil-brown type, terracotta brand with an olive accent. Softly rounded, diffusely shadowed, quietly luxurious \u2014 grounded, never rustic.",
